Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw hissed and kept her eyes locked onto the Predacons. All that the 
Maximal Shadow Wing was was a nuisance. The Predacons that were here may be 
the only ones that could take her to Megatron.

She took a step towards them. "Listen up you fools. Hold you're fire!"
